{"tid":1794201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[強國]  美國波音星際客機載人飛船重返地球","createTime":"2019-12-23T02:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T03:17:03.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f95e69834c52d5a77cc32a74646074c9a45aeada","tid":1794201,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:57:35.000Z","msg":"美國波音星際客機載人飛船重返地球<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1242410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D1242410&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=46b482dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1242410</a><br />\n<br />\n美國波音公司的&ldquo;星際客機&rdquo;載人飛船，重返地球，在美國新墨西哥州沙漠區著陸；今次是星際客機首次發射升空，艙內搭載一名假人用於試驗，飛船前日在卡納維拉爾角發射升空，但星箭分離後，飛船的太空鐘出現故障，以致未能進入預定軌道，無法按計劃在昨日與國際太空站會合，被迫取消原定為期7日的太空任務，提早4日返航。<br />\n<br />\n星際客機由波音與美國太空總署共同開發，原定明年接載太空人升空，但因今次故障，計劃可能受阻；美國太空穿梭機在8年前退役後，美國太空人往返國際太空站只能依賴俄羅斯飛船。為改變這個尷尬局面，美國大力發展商業載人航天飛船，分別研發載人版&ldquo;龍&rdquo;飛船及&ldquo;星際客機&rdquo;飛船。載人版&ldquo;龍&rdquo;飛船在今年3月完成不載人首飛，但4月進行地面測試時發生爆炸。"},{"pid":"bf7788ae64f89b0c7ef6b5bf2c8d15aa483fbac2","tid":1794201,"uid":114487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VgwZ4tD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVgwZ4tD.jpg&h=52b479a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGepv8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGepv8D.jpg&h=265d7544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocgLfAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocgLfAm.jpg&h=e2a8e121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d773bb5faae3b4e2a6b360a998e8d5fffa1e90ac","tid":1794201,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:58:50.000Z","msg":"藍絲牛閪飯臭西: 美國科技落後 無支付寶"},{"pid":"7a02e2a8a0a2dcf1e11f54c2705ccc4a4ad03ff7","tid":1794201,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:00:01.000Z","msg":"仲要係land陸地"},{"pid":"2c638587fd98bc64aef211e29576d9fffe244ce8","tid":1794201,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:01:52.000Z","msg":"波音又柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194d70c4ccec529381c3c8d0e9a78516de38e9cb","tid":1794201,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:02:17.000Z","msg":"波音好邪 樣樣出事"},{"pid":"0f8383aa123adaa5b9889f41e454c5e4e218f813","tid":1794201,"uid":36120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f95e69834c52d5a77cc32a74646074c9a45aeada","tid":1794201,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T02:57:35.000Z","msg":"美國波音星際客機載人飛船重返地球<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1242410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D1242410&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=46b482dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1242410</a><br />\n<br />\n美國波音公司的&ldquo;星際客機&rdquo;載人飛船，重返地球，在美國新墨西哥州沙漠區著陸；今次是星際客機首次發射升空，艙內搭載一名假人用於試驗，飛船前日在卡納維拉爾角發射升空，但星箭分離後，飛船的太空鐘出現故障，以致未能進入預定軌道，無法按計劃在昨日與國際太空站會合，被迫取消原定為期7日的太空任務，提早4日返航。<br />\n<br />\n星際客機由波音與美國太空總署共同開發，原定明年接載太空人升空，但因今次故障，計劃可能受阻；美國太空穿梭機在8年前退役後，美國太空人往返國際太空站只能依賴俄羅斯飛船。為改變這個尷尬局面，美國大力發展商業載人航天飛船，分別研發載人版&ldquo;龍&rdquo;飛船及&ldquo;星際客機&rdquo;飛船。載人版&ldquo;龍&rdquo;飛船在今年3月完成不載人首飛，但4月進行地面測試時發生爆炸。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:17:03.000Z","msg":"明明只係 space shuttle 發明之前都有嘅太空船一個，有咩咁特別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}